Lymbix-API

API wrapper of Lymbix. Support API version 2.2 .
See http://lymbix.com for more details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Lymbix::API

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Lymbix-API

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Lymbix-API

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Lymbix-API

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Lymbix-API/


